                            <comment id="236542" author="jfilizetti" created="Wed, 7 Nov 2018 12:27:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I tried again this morning with 2.10.5 and it seems to be working without the patch so we can close the bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="236453" author="jfilizetti" created="Tue, 6 Nov 2018 17:04:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think I still had the issue even with the patch from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5020&quot; title=&quot;OST can be all mounted successfully in parallel mount scenario&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5020&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5020&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&#160; I&apos;ll try to verify that in a the next day or two.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="236410" author="adilger" created="Tue, 6 Nov 2018 11:16:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is the patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/10229&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/10229&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5020&quot; title=&quot;OST can be all mounted successfully in parallel mount scenario&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5020&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5020&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; llite: don&apos;t reconnect MGC if connecting&quot; enough to fix this problem, or is &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/26839&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/26839&lt;/a&gt; still needed?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="193609" author="jfilizetti" created="Wed, 26 Apr 2017 15:54:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I believe this issue will affect master but the only system I have to test on was 2.5.3.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
